<title>Location</title>

<p>Open Help 2015 will be held at the historic
<link href="http://new.mercantilelibrary.com/">Mercantile Library</link>
at 414 Walnut St in downtown Cincinnati. Enter the building from the
Walnut St entrance, then take the first elevator to your left to the
eleventh floor.</p>

